This paper proposes a learning model for robot trajectory learning, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses policy search algorithms and hyperparameter tuning, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method involves updating the exploration rate to produce smooth trajectories, which is a topic related to control systems (cs.SY) and computer vision (cs.CV) for visual feedback in robot learning.
